{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/GIF_LogoNoRevealLoop_opaque__2_.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Electrifying_Hybrid.png?t=1692621118\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Hybrid-between-Shooter-and-Racing.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><strong>Charged! is a competitive, class-based third person shooter, with the intriguing skill based handling and controls of a racing game. Choose from a series of \u201cbattle-modified\u201d  radio-controlled cars, helicopters and aircraft and engage in dynamic battles over ressources (\u201cScrap\u201d) and control over objectives (\u201cCharge Stations\u201d) with up to 10 players.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/90s_Childhood_dreams.png?t=1692621118\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Childhooddreams-come-true.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><strong>Who didn\u2019t imagine equipping their RC-Vehicles with a nail gun, some firecrackers and new years rockets and having crazy battles with their friends in skateparks, malls or museums as a kid?! Isn\u2019t that part of what makes video games great, providing <br>experiences you otherwise never could?</strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Teams_are_alway_greater.png?t=1692621118\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Team-is-cool.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><strong>Whether on land or in the air, Charged! lives from its combined arms formula. Each vehicle has its own strengths,weaknesses and characteristics. Find the best way to support your team with your given toolkit and combine your unique abilities creatively to come out victorious!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Movement_wins.png?t=1692621118\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Movement-wins-Games.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><strong>The unique speeds, handling and movement capabilities of each vehicle, paired with verticality leads to a variety of intricate movement possibilities, and in itself is the foundation for a high skill ceiling and substantial gameplay depth and most importantly - a whole lot of fun!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Unique_is_not.png?t=1692621118\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/extras/Unique-is-not-unique-enough.gif?t=1692621118\" /><br><strong>Use the \u201cScrap\u201d your team gathered to further \u201cOvervolt\u201d your vehicle. Counteract weaknesses, amplify strengths or enhance your utility. You can upgrade your vehicle each round, so you can adjust to your team's needs and facilitate your preferred playstyle. Your game, your choice, play each class the way you want to play it!</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1692621118","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1692621118","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1692621118","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730010/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1692621118","categories":[{"description"